snippet.title: Celebs Speak Out On Johnny Depp And Amber Heard Divorce Drama
snippet.description:
The latest in Johnny Depp and Amber Heard’s divorce, as celebrity friends speak out in support of Johnny as Amber is seen laughing after meeting with her lawyer.
